    • Constructor Detail

      • Delivery

        public Delivery(java.lang.String rec,
                java.lang.String reg,
                int num,
                boolean ins)
        This constructor receives the basic details needed for the shipment, such as the recipient name, destination, nunber of items to be shipped, and if the customer wants the item to be insured.
        Parameters:
        rec - The name of the recipient (format: String)
        reg - The destination/region of the intended delivery (format: String)
        num - The number of items to be delivered (format: int)
        ins - whether the customer wants the parcel to be insured (format: boolean)
